Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鼻子呼出來的氣吹得我好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要勉強直連啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果阿拓的複製失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要從阿春那裡安裝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.28,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  你沒帶傳輸線過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪你沒有多一條長的傳輸線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  我最後再向你確認一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來要傳送給你的Brain  Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是個遊戲  但可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定哪天你會後悔今天所做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為這就能得到強大力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已經說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對力量才沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想告訴阿春和阿拓你們一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩遊戲就要玩得開心  不要每次都皺著眉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs14\an8\shad0\fad(300,300)}文件下載 — 安全警告\N是否運行程式BB2039？\N運行  取消
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕阿千會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  有我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  有你保護她肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不是說一定能安裝成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WELCOME  TO  THE  ACCELERATED  WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給胖豬下達今天的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還會做這種夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不換班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  還醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剛剛醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是好大的風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花都要被吹散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給你開好門的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你潛沉到我家的家庭伺服器來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  現在就去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接連接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Direct  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是奇蝦哦  是寒武紀的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在用那個虛擬角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(370,328)\fsp0}Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去換一個多好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經習慣這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  這個枕頭地…天堂是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧  之前為了慶祝我升上高年級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡增設了我的儲存容量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個解析度下  兩端之間有十五公里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  那也讓我玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓阿春進行配置的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定弄出一堆汽油和鐵罐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會到處都硝煙瀰漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡放些虎式戰車和Bf109戰鬥機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說今晚可能會做惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以害我睡不著覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做夢就創建不了對戰虛擬角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(400,328)\fsp0}Duel  Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說心理創傷會左右角色的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是完全沒心理創傷的人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話說得真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有心理創傷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說  小學遠足時…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰暈車  然後在我的膝蓋上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是枕頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想起從前  每當阿春來我家過夜時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿你當枕頭  我就一定能睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經是很久以前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為超頻連線者  我真的努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(293,328)\fsp0}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們的關係一定能修復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前那樣一起玩耍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  早！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我們能分到同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  真的好巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早會要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信在場的大多數人心中都是期待與不安參半
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是新生的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對尚未熟悉的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對尚未熟悉的高年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必一定會感到不適應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.09,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望各位能想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.92,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在你們後面神情坦然的高年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:45.52,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一兩年前也和你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.58,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣滿懷不安地站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:57.36,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年裡有三千一百五十三萬六千秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能想到  在台上說得頭頭是道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一個世界其實是秩序破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是連美國海軍陸戰隊也害怕的魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳  難道她猜到我在想什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間看似漫長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間看似漫長  實則轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家一定要充實地度過這一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的發言到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.09,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  有請生活指導老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:24.43,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們介紹在校內使用神經連接裝置時的注意事項
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說新生中有超頻連線者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該是發現什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐一直看著新生那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也那麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線者基本上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會和給自己安裝程式的上輩進同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是完全沒可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是先確認一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到新生拿到帳號登上校園網的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(315,328)\fsp0}Burst  Li…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個又偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的  你們想去加速世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以開始玩這遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想告訴你們遊戲要玩就要玩得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不一起玩的話就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  阿拓就當觀眾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要花費一點的超頻點數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(410,328)\fsp0}Burst  Point
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們順便看看阿千的對戰虛擬角色的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會向你提出挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是阿千的虛擬角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是叫Lime  Bell呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫Lime  Bell啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得顏色太花哨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩度那麼高的顏色可是很少見的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你是阿春？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛擬角色是心理創傷的現實反映啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那個就是阿拓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟阿春不同  和我想像的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  看來新生當中沒有超頻連線者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在名單中出現的就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver  Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cyan  Pile
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是Lime  Bell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別談這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是和阿春處於對戰狀態的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你知道規則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概的內容都從阿拓那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是贏多多的對戰  賺多多的點數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後升上Lv.10把遊戲通關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說還真的挺簡單啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼必殺技嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫面的這附近有體力計量條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡打開技能一覽表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是必殺技要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香櫞鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Citron  Call
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說要先把別人的話聽完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用必殺技先要蓄一定的計量條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己承受傷害或者對別人造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…破壞那邊的物件也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下得真狠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  Lime  Bell的體力沒有減少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工廠場地內破壞物件的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也會受到傷害才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為防禦力很高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是想說計量條應該蓄夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  早點跟我說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香櫞鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Citron  Call
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼都沒發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊  應該不會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是障眼法之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種寒酸的必殺技算什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  把你的必殺技給我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？這怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以幻覺系招式來說  計量條的消耗也太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既沒有造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有附加妨礙效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個鈴鐺敲一下阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想這麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害還不夠  再來兩次左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  再對阿春用一次必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香櫞鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Citron  Call
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的猜測沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力計量條在慢慢恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lime  Bell是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒術士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)\fsp0}Healer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒術士？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是治癒術士？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  阿拓也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我千萬不要公開  否則會引起騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓武的判斷很正確
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息一旦傳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有大量超頻連線者從東京各處聚集到杉並
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞她展開一場爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒術士有那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界開創整整七年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有治癒技能的超頻連線者僅出現過兩名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且其中一名因忍受不住自己成為爭端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而主動離開了加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說現在除了Lime  Bell之外只剩一名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個人現在已經位列六王之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六王之一？是什麼顏色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  現在我就連那個人的名字也不想向你提起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不希望你對那個人抱有一絲的好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我是相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕不會對其他的王產生興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕不會投靠其他的王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是這樣  我的內心依然很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪  你是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從過去到未來  你都是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠不會把你讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話離題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  治癒技能是加速世界的稀有技能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是擁有力量的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  倉嶋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在阿拓應該正在勸她不要草率行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我有必要和她敞開心扉好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐和阿千之間的交談…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會亂成一團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍團？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(315,328)\fsp0}Legion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我和阿春隸屬於黑暗星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(400,328)\fsp0}Nega  Nebulas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長是黑雪公主學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們三個又能像以前那樣在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的關係能修復吧  回復到以前那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要沖繩的禮物的話就跟我說一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級從下週日開始就進行修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的這段時間就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  倉嶋的事就要延後十天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那領土戰要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我死守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忍受敵人的旗幟插在杉並的土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下週防守成功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就答應你任何一個願望作為獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個果然是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要直連就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼出的氣會噴到她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁！我太差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家靜下來再想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確像是軍團長說出的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢  你還真冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們兩個打領土戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有其他辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就料想到遲早會出現這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我加入黑暗星雲的那一刻開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  阿千怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  她不是擁有治癒能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不戰鬥  但只要加入我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的關係能修復吧  回復到以前那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了？我不小心迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才被人拿下一局  目前比分是一比一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有以前那種壓倒性勝利的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他也在努力著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為他不再借助加速的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  在校內大賽拿不到冠軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒法打對外比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中腹部  勝負已分！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個學生  好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總決戰  紅隊  能美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白隊  黛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個新生是怎麼回事  總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！阿拓  把他砍翻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊  阿春也來加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼呀  聲音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中前臂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
