Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的一擊應該在攻擊範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不但避開攻擊而且反砍我一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經查那麼多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一直都沒有顯示出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才確實說了Burst…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻退出
